WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.140 --> 00:00:22.740
On a sunny day I'm happy

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:27.340
On a sunny day I smile

00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:30.400
Flowers bloom

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:33.500
In the sunlight

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:36.060
We play outside

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:42.160
And we go and look for butterflies

00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:50.040
On a rainy day I'm happy

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:55.360
On a rainy day I smile

00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:58.500
Hills and trees

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:01.160
Look fresh and green

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:03.940
And I see

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:10.660
Rainbow coloured umbrellas in the streets

00:01:13.820 --> 00:01:18.340
On a windy day I'm happy

00:01:19.340 --> 00:01:23.200
On a windy day I smile

00:01:24.060 --> 00:01:26.360
All the leaves

00:01:26.600 --> 00:01:29.000
Shake and fly

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.960
And my kite

00:01:32.860 --> 00:01:37.580
Is flying high in the sky

00:01:41.740 --> 00:01:46.080
On a snowy day I'm happy

00:01:47.380 --> 00:01:51.060
On a snowy day I smile

00:01:51.580 --> 00:01:53.880
Snowflakes fall

00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:56.880
On my window

00:01:57.340 --> 00:01:59.680
Frozen leaves

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:05.940
Shine like silver stars in a dream

